todo.message: Urgent-See a Doctor TODAY within 2-3 hours
Likely simple Urine Tract Infection if without fever or abdominal/loin pain. Consider antibiotics & see Dr if not better after 2 days
Wait up to 2 weeks - may consider backpocket antibiotics if not better after 10 days, esp with dark phlegm
Wait up to 2 weeks, abstain from sexual contact until your medical appointment
Wait up to 2 weeks, can consider physiotherapy in the meantime
